Schwartz Investment Trust - Schwartz Value Focused Fund Key Developments

Schwartz Value Focused Fund, Special/Extraordinary Shareholders Meeting, Jun 29, 2016
May 10 16
Schwartz Value Focused Fund, Special/Extraordinary Shareholders Meeting, Jun 29, 2016, at 10:00 US Eastern Standard Time. Location: Fund’s transfer agent, Ultimus Fund Solutions, LLC 225 Pictoria Drive, Suite 450 Cincinnati, OH 45246 United States Agenda: To approve the reclassification of the fund from a diversified fund to a non-diversified fund within the meaning of the Investment Company Act of 1940; to approve the removal of the fundamental investment limitation of the fund that prohibits it from investing more than 5% of its total assets in the securities of any one issuer (other than the United States Government, its agencies or instrumentalities); to approve the removal of the fundamental investment limitation of the fund that prohibits it from acquiring more than 10% of the outstanding voting securities of any one issuer; to approve the removal of the fundamental investment limitation of the fund that prohibits it from investing more than 10% of its total assets in the securities of unseasoned issuers or securities that are subject to legal or contractual restrictions on resale; and to transact any other business.


